{"tid":1097934,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖慎入) 有做緊美容院or做過嘅入嚟幫幫手","createTime":"2019-04-08T16:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T05:48:45.000Z","uid":152052,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"97dee0db0960fe8fca74b91e04328a5833f42f96","tid":1097934,"uid":152052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T16:41:12.000Z","msg":"小弟係中學既時候皮膚一直都好好 暗瘡都喺間中生幾粒<br />\n<br />\n但上到大專之後皮膚就一直好差 於是我上網睇咗啲建議<br />\n比如食A酸 針清 <br />\n<br />\n咁結果好明顯我就簡左針清啦  我仲去咗一間比好多連登仔推介既一間私人美容院 <br />\n<br />\n價錢個啲都唔講 去做左2個星期 d暗瘡的確如連登仔講既一樣 冇再生過岀嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n皮膚上見到有好多凹凸洞 但話明顯又唔明顯咁 冇去到馬國明既地步 <br />\n<br />\n有冇做開美容院既人 入嚟救下小弟 <br />\n<br />\n因為我仲有去個間到做 幫我做嗰嗰女仔話冇事 <br />\n<br />\n遲下會好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完全唔知信唔信佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下有圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DckOzWC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt